{"tid":2257392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS狂粉花百萬整容由白人變亞洲人　自誇「好多人以為我係智旻」","createTime":"2020-10-25T06:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T09:10:07.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":435,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b095d08e289997e818b8ab8b00c8d2b6e78e78fc","tid":2257392,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"如果是BTS的粉絲，相信都會認識「Oli London」這個來自英國的男生。今年30歲的他，在2013年愛上BTS後，就決意要整容變成智旻，6年間花了1億7千萬韓圜（約港元110萬）進行至少15項整容手術，欲由白人變為亞洲人。近日，他接受前女團Crayon Pop成員Way的訪問時表示，過去曾經在韓國街頭被多人認錯是智旻。<br />\n<br />\nOli London是在2013年沉迷於K-POP。當年，他到韓國短暫居住期間，怡巧遇上BTS出道。他被BTS的歌曲、舞姿深深吸引著，特別是他們「那近乎完美的外表」。於是，他決定要整容變成他的偶像智旻。在6年間，他走遍中國、韓國、阿美尼亞、波蘭等地，花費至少1億7千萬韓圜（約港元110萬），進行15項整容手術，和數百項非手術性的醫學程序。<br />\n<br />\n自稱英國首個K-pop歌手<br />\n<br />\nOli London最近接受前女團Crayon Pop成員Way於YouTube上的訪問。當時，他自稱自己是「英國首個K-pop歌手」，至今他已經發行了6首單曲。此外，他亦因為整容而成了名，近年他開設了自己的公關公司，同時亦是電視節目製作人。<br />\n<br />\n與紙牌智旻結婚<br />\n<br />\nOli表示，未整容前曾經因為外表而被多個女孩拒絕或者甩掉，令他感到非常自悲。為免再經歷被甩之痛，今年年初，他在拉斯維加斯舉行一個婚禮，與「紙牌公仔智旻」簽紙註冊，「紙牌不會背叛我！」<br />\n<br />\n對現時外表感滿意<br />\n<br />\nOli亦表示，除了曾經因為幾次整容後留下疤痕之外，基本上他都沒有後悔過整容，而且亦很滿意自己的外表。過去，他更曾經在韓國街頭被路人認錯為智旻本人，他亦為此感到十分高興。不過Way聽到後，忍不住質疑這句說話的真實性。<br />\n<br />\n網民狂酸<br />\n<br />\n雖然Oli大方承認自己多次整容，但「勇敢」的態度卻沒有得到網民認同。不少網民在Way的訪問影片下留言批評他，「只是一個有錢的失敗者」、「他根本不是BTS的粉絲，連成員都分辦不到」、「感覺Way一直都感到十分尷尬...真是辛苦了她」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWNuU4i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWNuU4i.jpg&h=513ee170&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGPk1Kj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGPk1Kj.jpg&h=e3bb0504&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAOxSQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAOxSQZ.jpg&h=7a5bca5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6a4JXF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6a4JXF.jpg&h=a94fa195&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWN6XhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWN6XhG.jpg&h=6dcdb1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtqXjv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtqXjv1.jpg&h=d1d837b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"144cd26be9dac3eb8bd87f9ec95d6947e50ee206","tid":2257392,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27d51d2713c4cdc5ac972e845041b68d5748bb8","tid":2257392,"uid":74065,"like":188,"dislike":24,"score":164,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"有95%似"},{"pid":"9e0dc20b6b6bbdde5766cbdc61c634fc64312c48","tid":2257392,"uid":44298,"like":222,"dislike":2,"score":220,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"成隻妖怪咁"},{"pid":"4ad5a251fb76265be7aad33f2e7da118d9eb1b2c","tid":2257392,"uid":127347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:32:09.000Z","msg":"Wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83673e20484f8d85f9991ada936ae65dc9fef5e6","tid":2257392,"uid":17866,"like":95,"dislike":15,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"9e0dc20b6b6bbdde5766cbdc61c634fc64312c48","tid":2257392,"uid":44298,"like":222,"dislike":2,"score":220,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"成隻妖怪咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"所以咪似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0808ec45de16cd39ef248866925bf6b31cf6724e","tid":2257392,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:35:37.000Z","msg":"cls..."},{"pid":"4a92c92f18314533db16dfcce7292ae20d3abf4f","tid":2257392,"uid":4574,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"蛇精男<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb7fb3d95f